Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User across all process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait - User when followed by Completed + Resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait - User compared to the duration of Accepted + Wait - Implementation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Accepted + In Progress to Accepted + Wait - User in variants containing Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total time between Accepted + Wait - User and Completed + Resolved in cases where Completed + In Call does not occur
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average cycle time of Accepted + Wait - User when it appears after Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Minimum time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants that transition directly to Completed + Resolved without intermediate waits
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Average time from Accepted + Wait - User to Completed + Closed in high-frequency variants (frequency > 100)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Total elapsed time between Accepted + Wait - User and the next occurrence of Accepted + In Progress in variants that loop back
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration of Accepted + Wait - User compared to Accepted + Wait - Vendor in variants ending with Completed + Closed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + Closed occurs

Name: Time from case start until Accepted + Wait - User in variants that include Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Average time between consecutive occurrences of Accepted + Wait - User within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Total time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants where it is immediately followed by Completed + Resolved
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Minimum cycle time of Accepted + Wait - User in variants that do not contain any other wait states
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait - User and the end of the case

Name: Average time from Accepted + Wait - User to Completed + In Call when Completed + In Call occurs after the wait
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Total duration of Accepted + Wait - User in cases handled by resources in France versus Brazil
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and the end of case grouped by the last value of resource country

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User when it appears before a second Queued + Awaiting Assignment
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Elapsed time between Accepted + Wait - User and the final Completed + Closed in long-running variants (performance > 1,000,000)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait - User' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait - User in variants that originate directly from Queued + Awaiting Assignment without prior Accepted + In Progress loops
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'
